{"tid":2415347,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華大基因成日有假陽性　間lab一直冇攞到認證　啲程序冇做過檢效","createTime":"2021-02-20T07:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T07:55:50.000Z","uid":261647,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"228280459ba73b8be88074a128496ad2ec7a549f","tid":2415347,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:32:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/posts/3967874936585543\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup%2Fposts%2F3967874936585543&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkjQSOVv8pHkqsyXWJi2kweQ%3D&h=daca01f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/posts/3967874936585543</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：前線科技人員<br />\n<br />\n尋日小編見到有位華大基因 lab technician 因為搖一搖啲 sample, 比 popo 拉咗，真係好驚，咩原來武漢肺炎病毒係搖出來嘅嗎？咁人類就真係好危險<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tdc/1/16/26a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ftdc%2F1%2F16%2F26a0.png&h=b9abaf52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過根據小編嘅認知，本來要由人體 sample extract 啲 RNA 出來，就要落 solvent 同做 centrifuge，所以其實搖咗一搖啲 sample 應該唔會影響啲結果，況且運送啲 sample 嘅過程都唔知搖咗幾多次，所以先要 double containers 嘛！<br />\n<br />\n對於華大基因成日都有假陽性結果，小編一啲都唔覺得意外，大半年前已經有記者報導過間 lab 無 HoKLas approval，過咗咁多月仍未攞到個 approval, 啲 SOP 根本冇人做過 validation，有 error 又有幾奇！<br />\n<br />\n777 成日話佢好關心香港人嘅健康，點解揀 lab 同疫苗都係揀啲 non-compliance 嘅比我哋呢？<br />\n<br />\n#武漢肺炎<br />\n<br />\nHOklas information:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.itc.gov.hk/ch/quality/hkas/conformity_assessment_bodies/hoklas_term_scope.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.itc.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fquality%2Fhkas%2Fconformity_assessment_bodies%2Fhoklas_term_scope.html&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkjQSOVv8pHkqsyXWJi2kweQ%3D&h=3a303663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.itc.gov.hk/ch/quality/hkas/conformity_assessment_bodies/hoklas_term_scope.html</a><br />\n<br />\nhttps://hk. appledaily. com/breaking/20210219/PJNIRZ7K2BGK7DNWEB6LBWR3ZU/<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0pp956c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0pp956c.jpg&h=be642ff9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96a3f4a8090fb2c8a0bcffd5818a32de2dcaea61","tid":2415347,"uid":267423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8690b4bd75d9527e461056ab6a3a933a3b9bba52","tid":2415347,"uid":32667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115216f61f6e442c3c613c33ddd1a44fcbbd17fe","tid":2415347,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004ee25cc8512173a99b90f3cec8325dba5a46ee","tid":2415347,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275a47a79a3c2e4677821863e19c30849e3f1cd3","tid":2415347,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:48:36.000Z","msg":"出事咪搵個替死鬼<br />\n賴話搖過個樣本<br />\n明明係測試質素問題"},{"pid":"d99d88337f05bd4f82f1f0a41cf1654b3df8290b","tid":2415347,"uid":54125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:52:20.000Z","msg":"搖下都可以變陽性<br />\n你就知幾準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e5d7eb5c9f0314477f001d40a8b8